Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.dvcs

Class DVCSRequest

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.dvcs.DVCSMessage
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.dvcs.DVCSRequest
public class DVCSRequest
extends DVCSMessage
DVCRequest is general request to DVCS (RFC 3029). It represents requests for all types of services. Requests for different services differ in DVCData structure.
